,190,120,7],[589112,146,71,6],[851317,89,72,7]]},{"type":"character","term":"Lea Han","aliases":[],"excerpt":"Lea Han was the oldest of them, Baltiel's senior by two years, and her maths was faultless at very short notice.","locs":[[32988,128,30,4],[35528,102,17,3],[35729,112,0,7],[35842,89,56,3],[37551,115,41,4],[40396,182,0,3],[42142,122,69,5],[47365,89,14,3],[48782,96,12,4],[50462,162,5,3],[51395,121,0,3],[52182,197,0,3],[52940,104,0,3],[53277,122,11,3],[53554,202,20,3],[53786,141,0,3],[54338,78,55,3],[54842,133,0,3],[55294,86,22,3],[55714,189,0,5],[55985,109,0,3],[56726,103,43,3],[57111,126,76,3],[57944,181,6,3],[77875,148,34,3],[80528,96,0,4],[87376,135,58,3],[89003,85,27,4],[96975,173,0,4,5,4],[111041,176,142,4],[182708,132,0,3],[192584,210,0,3],[402361,129,65,3],[544848,187,85,3]]},{"type":"topic","term":"Old Empire","aliases":[],"excerpt":"The Old Empire is at the root of it all, meaning some common ground at least. If we had met something genuinely alien, we wouldn't know where to start.","locs":[[132389,174,117,10],[132877,248,81,12],[156397,151,4,10],[178423,165,67,10],[247032,137,86,10],[259944,205,143,10],[262358,207,119,10],[278292,131,52,10],[278928,214,106,10],[280436,139,15,10],[308389,182,77,10],[425560,142,132,10],[439546,93,54,10],[444384,188,149,10],[465308,127,45,10],[469342,106,66,12],[469524,186,47,10],[470045,191,148,10],[473780,202,146,10],[476796,128,108,10],[478558,232,59,12],[515168,93,21,10],[528173,176,147,10],[531196,100,34,10],[614979,175,73,11,106,10],[663540,256,123,10],[674910,91,75,10],[729943,111,52,10],[730569,91,49,10],[730846,255,39,10],[751173,165,145,10],[751489,96,3,10],[841607,146,10,10]]},{"type":"character","term":"Noah","aliases":[],"excerpt":"Another octopus, a male. Perhaps his designation, set down in the old human-style databanks, is Noah.","locs":[[607377,101,96,5],[607479,141,78,4],[608622,88,16,5],[608873,141,0,4],[610023,251,87,5],[611122,224,28,4],[612449,214,0,4],[612664,45,0,4],[613238,123,0,4],[614210,177,1